'''Charbote root''' was a [[Vegetable/Legends|vegetable]] used in many [[Corellia/Legends|Corellian]] dishes.

It was served at the Corellian food outlet on [[Skip 1]] in the [[Smuggler's Run/Legends|Smuggler's Run]].

